description:
God's Judgment - Most Christians don't understand that this event is happening right now! How will God judge me? Are you prepared to stand before your Maker?  This video will provide you with critical facts about the phase of the judgment that is taking place right now - before the second coming of Jesus! In fact, it is so important that it will decide who will be lost, and who will inherit eternal life. Where will this judgment happen? Who will be involved? What evidence will be considered? What will be the standard on which we will all be judged? What is Jesus doing right now in Heaven? How can you make it through Gods judgment and be pronounced innocent? Everything is at stake. Your eternal destiny hangs in the balance! You dont want to miss this message!
